French defense attacking ideas on the kingside.} Bh5 (12... Bf5 13. a3 (13. Nb3
Nb4 14. Re2 Bd3 $11) 13... Nge7 14. b4 Bg6 15. Nb3 Nf5 16. Bb2 Be7 17. Rc1 O-O
18. Nc5 $14) 13. Nb3 Bb4 (13... Nge7 14. g4 Bg6 15. Nc5 Qc7 16. Be3 h5 17. Rc1
hxg4 18. hxg4 {and White's chances are more to be preferred}) 14. Re3 Nge7 15.
a3 Ba5 16. Nc5 Rb8 17. b4 Bb6 18. g4 Bg6 19. Rc3 {with a stable plus for White,
although Black is very solid} *

