{And not only Black has an eternal weakness on d6, but it's also
straightforward for White to start an assault at the kingside.} Rd8 13. Rhg1
Qc8 14. f4 $16 {[%csl Re8][%cal Gf4f5,Gh2h5] 1-0 (33) Rublevsky,S (2650)
