d4 and trade queens, sometimes maneuver Nf6-d7-c5 becomes a possibility. Which
rooks to put where, when is the right moment to execute all of the previously
mentioned ideas - all of these questions are not so easy to answer for Black
who is looking for the perfect defense.} Nd7 {Should he? A good question -
