Rfd1 Nh6 21. bxc4 $14 {[%cal Gc3e4,Ge4d6] and White is slightly better}) 15.
Nd5 $1 {[%cal Gd5b6] because of the fork threat on b6 the game becomes forced.}
Nxd5 (15... Rc5 16. Rac1 bxc4 17. bxc4 {doesn't feel as an improvement for
