later. Otherwise, the weakness on c6 could have serious consequences when the
e5 knight is chased away.} 17. dxe6 (17. f4 $5 exd5 18. fxe5 dxe5 19. Nf3 dxe4
20. Ng5 f5 $13) 17... fxe6 18. Rad1 Nc6 19. Qf2 $5 $146 {my suggested a game
plan which appears to be a novelty. White simply plans to double the rooks on
